Mushindu mupepele wa kuenza ngendu mu mulongo wa kumpala anyi mu mulongo wa kumpala ngua kufuta makuta a bungi bua diakalenga edi (anyi kulekela bena mudimu banuenzelawu).
Kadi kabitu anu bipepele to: udi mua kutekemena bua kufuta misangu inayi anyi dikumi ne umue bua kusumba ndeke wa mushinga mukole kupita ndeke wa mushinga mukese!
Mu kuamba kuimpe, kabiena ne mushinga nansha mukese bua kukeba makuta a bungi bua kupeta muaba mu tshibambalu tshia malu a bungenda anyi tshia diambedi mu ndeke idi kayiyi ne njila wa ndeke wa kumbukila ku A uya ku B.
